QUERY_CLOB:
select case when 1=1
            then 'N'
            else 'Y'
            end pass_yn,
       aa.workspace,
       aa.application_id, 
       null page_id,
       aa.created_by,
       aa.created_on,
       aa.last_updated_by,
       aa.last_updated_on,
       apex_string.format('Application `%0` (app %1) blerg', 
        p0 => aa.application_name, 
        p1 => aa.application_id) validation_failure_message,
       apex_string.format('Application `%0` (app %1) blerg', 
        p0 => aa.application_name, 
        p1 => aa.application_id) issue_title,
       aa.application_id component_id,
       null parent_component_id,
       aa.application_name,
       aa.alias,
       aa.availability_status
from apex_applications aa
where aa.workspace = svt_preferences.get_preference ('SVT_DEFAULT_WORKSPACE')
and aa.application_id = 17000033
